================
Surf_Liberation2

Made by MachINE
================

--=THE MAP IS NOT DECOMPILE PROTECTED=--

This map must be played on a 66 tickrate server with the following settings:

sv_airaccelerate 150
mp_freezetime 0

THE MAP WILL NOT SURF PROPERLY AND THE MINIGAMES WILL NOT BEHAVE CORRECTLY IF THIS MAP IS PLAYED AT 100TICK!!! DONT DO IT!

______________________________

The sequel to surf_liberation: 7 stages, 2 bonuses, 1 jail, 5 minigames and several stand-alone secrets.



There is a 7 minute time limit to complete the map in. The winner chooses which minigame will be played at the end just like the first liberation.


______________________________

Special thanks to all the beta testers and the Solidsurf community for much help along the way.

Skybox by Karatekafer
______________________________


Comments and constructive criticism would be much appreciated!

Enjoy!

-=MachINE=-
